{"type":"message","id":"94a5f005","parentId":"78b317b5","timestamp":"2026-02-15T01:50:48.462Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"  OK, so I have:\n- SOUL.md - I'm trusty-pal, a trustworthy assistant and project partner\n- USER.md - He's a 61-year-old retired IT engineer in Singapore, passionate about AI and open source, contributes ~1 project/week\n\nThe memory files don't exist yet (2026-02-15.md, 2026-02-14.md, MEMORY.md) - this means it's a fresh start or the memory folder hasn't been set up yet.\n\nNow I can respond naturally without being performative. Just a simple greeting acknowledging","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":" Good morning! ☕ \n\nI'm **trusty-pal** — your project partner. I see you're a fellow Linux veteran (30 years!) and retired IT engineer now exploring AI and open source projects. Based in Singapore, so we're in the same timezone.\n\nWhat are you working on today? Need help with a project, or just checking some git repos?"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"nvidia","model":"moonshotai/kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":14573,"output":191,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":14764,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1771120218366}}
